Sample_treatment_protocol_ch1: DMSO and E2 conditions were subjected to DMSO or E2 treatment for 6h
Sample_growth_protocol_ch1: Cells were seeded in full media; the following day media was changed to either estrogen depleted media (for DMSO and E2 groups) or same DMEM/F12 50/50 full media (for FM); cells were incubated for 72h; the day of cell harvesting media was refreshed
Sample_extract_protocol_ch1: Cells were snap frozen and RNA was extracted with RNeasy Kit from Qiagen (#74106), DNase treatment was performed during the extraction, Libraries were performed by Genewiz
Sample_data_processing: RNA-seq reads were filtered for quality and 3' trimmed for adapter sequences using trimgalore, Reads were aligned to mouse assembly hg38 using STAR (v2.6.0a) with default parameters., Read count tables were created using HTSeq v0.9.1., To create density files, the signal was normalised using the scalefactors from DESeq2 converted to BigWig using BEDTools.
Supplementary_files_format_and_content: BigWig files containing read densities normalized using DESeq2

Sample_data_processing: RNA-seq reads were filtered for quality and 3' trimmed for adapter sequences using trimgalore, Reads were aligned to mouse assembly hg38 using STAR (v2.6.0a) with default parameters., Read count tables were created using HTSeq v0.9.1., To create density files, the signal was normalised using the scalefactors from DESeq2 converted to BigWig using BEDTools.
Supplementary_files_format_and_content: BigWig files containing read densities normalized using DESeq2
